Subject: [PATCH 1/1] configure: take MAKEFLAGS from the command-line

Autospec can't set it in the environment

Change-Id: I869fa813913644eb81b0fffd1512b55d0275e1c1
---
 configure | 5 +++++
 1 file changed, 5 insertions(+)

diff --git a/configure b/configure
index 41fc9575a0..1998d3858b 100755
--- a/configure
+++ b/configure
@@ -121,6 +121,11 @@ for i in "$@"; do
 $a"
             done
             ;;
+        MAKEFLAGS=*)
+            eval "$i"
+            export MAKEFLAGS
+            continue        # Don't save and don't let qmake see it
+            ;;
         *)
             OPT_CMDLINE="$OPT_CMDLINE
 $i"
